release_note: Added support for the Japan and Canada regions. Performance improvements and bug fixes.
Added support for generic files sharing via messaging. Added online offline status for interlocutors. Bug fixes and performance improvements.
Added device verification when logging into the app
Enables users to download media from secure storage to devices Performance improvements and bug fixes
KeeperChat is now 100 FREE for personal use! We ve also fixed several bugs.

Our latest update introduces GIF animated graphic capabilities. You can now search and send GIFs to your contacts directly from your keyboard. In addition to GIF capabilities version 2.4 includes performance improvements and bug fixes.

Our latest update introduces new security features added family plan support and improved KeeperChat Business capabilities. Blur your chats for maximum security with Stealth Mode. Protect the content you and your family share with our new KeeperChat Family Plan and Keeper Family Bundle. Easily create conversations between co workers and teams. Update your app now to take advantage of all these exciting features. Need help Contact support keepersecurity.com.

KeeperChat 2.1.0 is here! With this version we re excited to introduce increased customization and usability of the app including: Edit previously sent messages Rename group chats Assign conversation avatars Upload photos directly from your phone s gallery Save drafted messages Edit contact profiles Copy and paste messages Performance Improvements Update your app today to start using these awesome new features! We re excited to let you know that Keeper Enterprise customers can now log in to KeeperChat with your existing Keeper Password Manager account! We ve added support for role enforcement policies additional two factor authentication methods such as DUO and RSA and integration with your existing Enterprise SSO solution. Please contact sales keepersecurity.com to activate KeeperChat on your Keeper Business or Keeper Enterprise account today!
